data.description: Come experience this charming 1950's Brick Home, sold as is, and craft your own story within its cozy walls! Main level master and bath. Keep warm and cozy during chilly winter nights by any of the three fireplaces, adding that touch of homely comfort to your days. Separate library/office area with cozy fireplace, turn this space into whatever suits your lifestylea private library, an office, or an extra cozy bedroom. A 22x24 detached garage/workshop with an equipment shed calls out to the DIY enthusiast, offering ample space for projects or storage needs. Step out onto the 26x31 back brick patio, an inviting space for outdoor gatherings. unfinished basement with a backup wood stove in ductwork. Note a current roof leak in the kitchen. Basement refrigerator not included. Washer and dryer not part of the sale. However, the upstairs fridge, oven, and dishwasher will convey, though the dishwasher is non-operational. Creek at rear of property walnut trees out back, large back yard.
